{
  "stem": "18626.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it signaled more the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we saw bomb-- the airplanes all the time, we had to run.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans had to run, and we were left without guards in the working place, we knew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans were so nasty that times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They knew they are losing the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were counting the days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know what's going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We still thought that if they lose-- if-- before the Americans are going to liberate us or whoever is going to liberate us, the Germans are going to shoot us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what the plan was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The plan was all the prisoners from all the camps to be shot before the liberation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But thank God it didn't work out that way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Instead, the main chief who had the order to liquidate all the prisoners from Dachau didn't give out the order.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He want to save his own life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He knew the war is lost.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he figured if the Americans come in and he'll show that he had the order to shoot all the prisoners and he didn't release it, he's not going to be hung.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's not going to be punished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's how we were saved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think his name was Martin Weiss.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The prisoners, after the-- we were all chased for the dead march from Dachau all the way to the Tyrol mountains in big caves, natural caves.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the prisoners from all the camps all around, not only Dachau, were placed in that valley, a natural valley near the Tyrol mountains.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe three, four miles valley.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Deep.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You go deep and deep and deep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all the machine guns were placed all on the top, ready to fire and shoot at people.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
